          <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M10 0l3 7 7 1-5 5 1 7-6-3-6 3 1-7-5-5 7-1z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" style="opacity:0.8"><path d="M10 0l3 7 7 1-5 5 1 7-6-3-6 3 1-7-5-5 7-1z"/></svg>
        </span>
