        <h2 id="verdict">Is RankMath worth it in 2026? Final verdict</h2>
        <p><strong>For any WordPress site owner: yes — install it today.</strong> The free version covers more than Yoast Premium for $0. If you have ever paid Yoast $99/yr per site, RankMath Pro at $95/yr for unlimited sites is the easiest yes in WordPress plugins.</p>

